(8, '-paint-the-house-walls', 'Elena', ' Paint the house walls', '<pre id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\" data-fulltext=\"\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">You like the rooms with a touch of color, but you do not finish deciding on one tone or another ... Warm or cold? Intense or discreet? These keys will help you choose what color to paint your house</span></pre>', '<h5 id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">You like the rooms with a touch of color, but you do not finish deciding on one tone or another ... Warm or cold? Intense or discreet? These keys will help you choose what color to paint your house .</span></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><strong><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">THE DIMENSIONS DECIDE &nbsp;</span></strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">If the room is small, it is best to choose colors that are not too intense. And better cold than warm. The ideal wall to paint color? The one with the windows to let the light fall on the white ones.</span></h5>', 7, '2019-04-14 20:05:43', 'dry, pastle, painting', '00474463_115712fc_1577x2000.jpg', 'PUBLISHED', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL),
(9, 'childrens-rooms', 'Elena', 'CHILDREN\'S ROOMS', '<pre id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\" data-fulltext=\"\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">Children\'s rooms for babies and children who sleep alone or in a shared room. Here you will find the most original decoration keys and ideas.</span></pre>', '<h5 id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">Do you want to refresh your bedroom? Color is one of the most effective elements to achieve this and you do not even have to paint the walls. Just a few small touches. Bedding is one of the most important points for the aesthetics of the bedroom.</span></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\"> We can combine sheets, covers and quilts with different patterns: large, small, geometric, floral ... Everything is valid as long as blue dominates.</span></h5>', 6, '2019-04-14 21:34:28', 'dry, pastle', 'fotomesita_b3da912d_1000x562.jpg', 'PUBLISHED', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL),
(10, '-decorative-dilems:-large-tiles-vs-small', 'Elena', ' DECORATIVE DILEMS: LARGE TILES VS SMALL', '<pre id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\" data-fulltext=\"\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">Are you going to reform your bathroom? Your kitchen? Do you want to change the tiles and do not know what would be better? Big without joints? Small subway type? Here are some keys that will help you decide</span></pre>', '<h5 id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><strong><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">SMALL TILES FOR OPEN KITCHENS</span></strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">In a kitchen open to the dining room, small tiles are a good option. You can place them only on the parapet and paint the rest of the space so that the different rooms are better integrated. If you choose the tiles of the same color as the painting, the effect will be much more harmonious. </span></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><strong><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">LARGE TILES EXTEND </span></strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">Especially if they have a rectified board. The borada between pieces is not perceived and this creates the effect of being a continuous surface, and a continuous surface always creates the illusion that the surface is larger than it actually is. If, in addition, they are tiles with brightness like these, the sensation of amplitude is bigger.</span></h5>', 6, '2019-04-14 20:30:23', 'renovation', 'cocina-con-azulejos-grandes-00423816_4bbbbadd_1500x2000.jpg', 'PUBLISHED', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL);

