(88, 1, 8, 'entries', 'Elena', NULL, '{\"Tabla\":\"entries\",\"Data\":{\"permalink\":\"-paint-the-house-walls\",\"author\":\"Elena\",\"title\":\" Paint the house walls\",\"abstract\":\"\\u003Cpre id=\\u0022tw-target-text\\u0022 class=\\u0022tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\\u0022 dir=\\u0022ltr\\u0022 data-placeholder=\\u0022Traducci\\u0026oacute;n\\u0022 data-fulltext=\\u0022\\u0022\\u003E\\u003Cspan lang=\\u0022en\\u0022 tabindex=\\u00220\\u0022\\u003EYou like the rooms with a touch of color, but you do not finish deciding on one tone or another ... Warm or cold? Intense or discreet? These keys will help you choose what color to paint your house\\u003C\\/span\\u003E\\u003C\\/pre\\u003E\",\"content\":\"\\u003Ch5 id=\\u0022tw-target-text\\u0022 class=\\u0022tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\\u0022 dir=\\u0022ltr\\u0022 data-placeholder=\\u0022Traducci\\u0026oacute;n\\u0022\\u003E\\u003Cspan lang=\\u0022en\\u0022 tabindex=\\u00220\\u0022\\u003EYou like the rooms with a touch of color, but you do not finish deciding on one tone or another ... Warm or cold? Intense or discreet? These keys will help you choose what color to paint your house .\\u003C\\/span\\u003E\\u003C\\/h5\\u003E\\r\\n\\u003Ch5 class=\\u0022tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\\u0022 dir=\\u0022ltr\\u0022 data-placeholder=\\u0022Traducci\\u0026oacute;n\\u0022\\u003E\\u003Cstrong\\u003E\\u003Cspan lang=\\u0022en\\u0022 tabindex=\\u00220\\u0022\\u003ETHE DIMENSIONS DECIDE \\u0026nbsp;\\u003C\\/span\\u003E\\u003C\\/strong\\u003E\\u003C\\/h5\\u003E\\r\\n\\u003Ch5 class=\\u0022tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\\u0022 dir=\\u0022ltr\\u0022 data-placeholder=\\u0022Traducci\\u0026oacute;n\\u0022\\u003E\\u003Cspan lang=\\u0022en\\u0022 tabindex=\\u00220\\u0022\\u003EIf the room is small, it is best to choose colors that are not too intense. And better cold than warm. The ideal wall to paint color? The one with the windows to let the light fall on the white ones.\\u003C\\/span\\u003E\\u003C\\/h5\\u003E\",\"date\":\"2019-04-14 20:05:15\",\"tags\":\"dry, pastle, painting\",\"idCategoria\":\"7\",\"status\":\"DRAFT\",\"image\":\"00474463_115712fc_1577x2000.jpg\"},\"id\":8}', '2019-04-14 08:05:15', 'http://localhost/colores/', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/73.0.3683.86 Safari/537.36', NULL),
