but you do not finish deciding on one tone or another ... Warm or cold? Intense or discreet? These keys will help you choose what color to paint your house</span></pre>,[content] => <h5 id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">You like the rooms with a touch of color, but you do not finish deciding on one tone or another ... Warm or cold? Intense or discreet? These keys will help you choose what color to paint your house .</span></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><strong><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">THE DIMENSIONS DECIDE &nbsp;</span></strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Traducci&oacute;n\"><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">If the room is small, it is best to choose colors that are not too intense. And better cold than warm. The ideal wall to paint color? The one with the windows to let the light fall on the white ones.</span></h5>,[date] => 2019-04-14 20:05:43,[tags] => dry, pastle, painting,[idCategoria] => 7,[status] => PUBLISHED,', '2019-04-14 08:04:43', 'http://localhost/colores/', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/73.0.3683.86 Safari/537.36', NULL),
