(92, 1, 9, 'entries', 'Elena', NULL, '{\"Tabla\":\"entries\",\"Data\":{\"permalink\":\"-children\\u0027s-rooms\",\"author\":\"Elena\",\"title\":\" CHILDREN\\u0027S ROOMS\",\"abstract\":\"\\u003Cpre id=\\u0022tw-target-text\\u0022 class=\\u0022tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\\u0022 dir=\\u0022ltr\\u0022 data-placeholder=\\u0022Traducci\\u0026oacute;n\\u0022 data-fulltext=\\u0022\\u0022\\u003E\\u003Cspan lang=\\u0022en\\u0022 tabindex=\\u00220\\u0022\\u003EChildren\\u0027s rooms for babies and children who sleep alone or in a shared room. Here you will find the most original decoration keys and ideas.\\u003C\\/span\\u003E\\u003C\\/pre\\u003E\",\"content\":\"\\u003Ch5 id=\\u0022tw-target-text\\u0022 class=\\u0022tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\\u0022 dir=\\u0022ltr\\u0022 data-placeholder=\\u0022Traducci\\u0026oacute;n\\u0022\\u003E\\u003Cspan lang=\\u0022en\\u0022 tabindex=\\u00220\\u0022\\u003EDo you want to refresh your bedroom? Color is one of the most effective elements to achieve this and you do not even have to paint the walls. Just a few small touches. Bedding is one of the most important points for the aesthetics of the bedroom.\\u003C\\/span\\u003E\\u003C\\/h5\\u003E\\r\\n\\u003Ch5 class=\\u0022tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\\u0022 dir=\\u0022ltr\\u0022 data-placeholder=\\u0022Traducci\\u0026oacute;n\\u0022\\u003E\\u003Cspan lang=\\u0022en\\u0022 tabindex=\\u00220\\u0022\\u003E We can combine sheets, covers and quilts with different patterns: large, small, geometric, floral ... Everything is valid as long as blue dominates.\\u003C\\/span\\u003E\\u003C\\/h5\\u003E\",\"date\":\"2019-04-14 20:17:38\",\"tags\":\"dry, pastle\",\"idCategoria\":\"6\",\"status\":\"DRAFT\",\"image\":\"fotomesita_b3da912d_1000x562.jpg\"},\"id\":9}', '2019-04-14 08:17:38', 'http://localhost/colores/', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/73.0.3683.86 Safari/537.36', NULL),
